      (1097, 26, 4, 0, N'NS Baron G5B', N'Nanite Systems'' first attempts into close-range weaponry resulted in the powerful Baron G5. The tube fed Baron is able to put down targets at longer ranges than typical shotguns thanks to its narrow choke.', NULL, 1, 14645),
