      (1979, 26, 11, 0, N'Parsec VX3-A', N'Built from a highly-tinkered Parallax, the Parsec was the brainchild of a small group of engineers looking for long-range perfection. Though significantly louder than most sniper rifles, it drops targets before the sound wave even reaches them.', 1, 1, 79811),
