      (7232, 26, 6, 0, N'EM1', N'Esamir Munition Corporation''s EM1 LMG is a unique mix of high ammo count and fast reloading time, allowing the shooter to control firing lanes with little downtime. NC use only.', 2, 1, 5337),
      (7233, 26, 6, 0, N'GD-22S', N'Genudine Dynamics developed the 22S as a possible replacement for the NC6 SAW. In comparison to the SAW, it features a faster firing rate and reload time, but is limited by a 50-round detachable box magazine. NC use only.', 2, 1, 5340),
      (7234, 26, 6, 0, N'NC6S Gauss SAW S', N'The NC6S Gauss SAW''s select fire mode gives it incredible adaptability on the field. NC use only.', 2, 1, 5343),
      (7235, 26, 6, 0, N'EM6', N'The EM6''s incredible adaptability on the field makes it popular among NC soldiers. NC use only.', 2, 1, 85856),
      (7236, 26, 6, 0, N'LA1 Anchor', N'The LA1 Anchor is tuned for close quarters effectiveness. It features high damage, moderate rate of fire, advanced laser attachments, and a 50 round box magazine for quick combat reloads. NC use only.', 2, 1, 9449),
      (7253, 26, 6, 0, N'T9 CARV-S', N'This special, versatile variant of the CARV can adapt to nearly any situation thanks to its multiple firing modes and wide range of attachments. Compared to its predecessor, it features a slightly slower rate of fire and more controllable recoil. TR use only.', 3, 1, 5382),
      (7254, 26, 6, 0, N'MSW-R', N'The MSW-R was designed to meet the needs of mobile Terran Republic shock troopers. Its light weight and fast reload time allows forward soldiers to push forward without stopping. TR use only.', 3, 1, 9458),
      (7255, 26, 6, 0, N'T16 Rhino', N'The T16 Rhino was designed as a squad support weapon that remains accurate, even during sustained fire. TR use only.', 3, 1, 9461),
      (7256, 26, 6, 0, N'TMG-50', N'Designed with distance and accuracy in mind, the TMG-50''s manageable recoil allows it to outperform other LMGs at long range. TR use only.', 3, 1, 85859),
      (7257, 26, 6, 0, N'T32 Bull', N'Developed for a mix of close quarters combat and point defense, the T32 Bull features both balanced recoil and high maneuverability. TR use only.', 3, 1, 9464),
