      (7275, 26, 6, 0, N'Pulsar LSW', N'The Pulsar Light Support Weapon (LSW) is a Pulsar variant with a high capacity battery and heavier barrel. Its reputation as a highly versatile weapon makes it a popular choice for missions where anything can happen. VS use only.', 1, 1, 85862),
      (7276, 26, 6, 0, N'SVA-88', N'The SVA-88''s overclocked discharge coil allows it to fire plasma at a higher velocity than most weapons in its class. When firing at long distances, the user will need to lead targets much less than usual. VS use only.', 1, 1, 6030),
      (7277, 26, 6, 0, N'Flare VE6', N'Vanu Esamir''s AdvWep labs designed the heavy-hitting Flare VE6 to pack the most punch per shot. In the hands of an experience marksman, the Flare can wreak havoc on enemy infantry at close to medium ranges. VS use only.', 1, 1, 6030),
      (7278, 26, 6, 0, N'Ursa', N'The Ursa features manageable recoil and a high velocity projectile, making it extremely effective at ranges beyond that of other LMGs. VS use only.', 1, 1, 9473),
      (7301, 26, 11, 0, N'AF-8 RailJack', N'Cutting edge railgun tech found in Auraxis'' Firearms Railjack sniper rifle allows for lightning-fast bullet velocities. Distant targets are dropped almost instantly following a split-second charge-up delay from its powerful superconductor.', 2, 1, 13752),
      (7316, 26, 11, 0, N'TRAP-M1', N'The TRAP-M1 can switch between short-range 3-round burst and long-range 2-round burst firing modes, allowing for incredible flexibility on the battlefield.', 3, 1, 13755),
      (7337, 26, 11, 0, N'Phaseshift VX-S', N'Equipped with an experimental regenerating power core, the Phaseshift VX-S has no use for traditional ammunition, and can switch between semi-auto and bolt-action firing modes to fit the engagement range. VS use only.', 1, 1, 13758),
